The paper discusses the application of deep learning on 3D data for tasks such as segmentation, recognition, and correspondence. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses different 3D data representations, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the challenges of applying deep learning on 3D data, which could fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
